properties.areaDesc: Teller County/Rampart Range above 7500fT/Pike's Peak Between 7500 And 11000 Ft; Pikes Peak above 11000 Ft
properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued February 7 at 8:49AM MST until February 7 at 5:00PM MST by NWS Pueblo CO
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow. Additional snow accumulations of 1 to 4
inches...heaviest across northern Teller County. Winds gusting
as high as 35 mph.

* WHERE...Teller County...the Rampart Range and Pikes Peak.

* WHEN...Until 5 PM MST this afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Plan on slick and snowpacked road conditions. The
hazardous conditions could impact the evening commute.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

The latest road conditions for the state you are calling from can
be obtained by calling 5 1 1.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 5 PM MST THIS AFTERNOON
